ITV2在2007年獲得廣播數位獎的年度頻道獎<ref>{{cite web |last=Oatts |first=Joanne |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/media/news/a59878/itv2-named-channel-of-the-year.html |title=ITV2 named channel of the year |work=Digital Spy |date=2007-06-07 |access-date=2007-06-07 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924053023/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/media/news/a59878/itv2-named-channel-of-the-year.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在2013年再次獲獎<ref>{{cite web |last=Kanter |first=Jake |url=http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/home/broadcast-digital-awards/itv2-wins-channel-of-the-year/5057979.article |title=ITV2 wins Channel of the Year |publisher=Broadcast |date=2013-07-03 |access-date=2013-09-02 |archive-date=2020-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627021736/https://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/home/broadcast-digital-awards/itv2-wins-channel-of-the-year/5057979.article |dead-url=no }}</ref>。ITV2還在2007年的[[愛丁堡國際電視節|愛丁堡國際電視節]]上獲得年度非無線電視頻道獎<ref>{{cite web |last=Wilkes |first=Neil |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/media/news/a73834/bbc-one-named-channel-of-the-year.html |title=BBC One named Channel of the Year |work=Digital Spy |date=2007-08-25 |access-date=2007-08-25 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924053105/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/media/news/a73834/bbc-one-named-channel-of-the-year.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==批評==
2014年，ITV2因《{{link-en|Dapper Laughs: On the Pull|Dapper Laughs: On the Pull}}》節目而受到爭議。該節目因宣傳對女性的暴力而受到批評<ref>{{cite web |last= |first= |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/newsbeat-29980142 |title=Dapper Laughs apologises over 'sexist' homeless jokes |work=BBC news |date=2014-11-09 |access-date=2021-06-28 |archive-date=2021-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210628145939/https://www.bbc.com/news/newsbeat-29980142 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一份要求停播該節目的請願書有多達68,210人簽字<ref>{{cite web|last=|first=|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/voices/comment/clicktivism-works-just-ask-julien-blanc-and-dapper-laughs-9860770.html|title=Julien Blanc and Dapper Laughs have learnt about the power of clicktivism the hard way|work=Independent|date=2014-11-14|access-date=2021-06-28|archive-date=2021-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210628145940/https://www.independent.co.uk/voices/comment/clicktivism-works-just-ask-julien-blanc-and-dapper-laughs-9860770.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。ITV未續約該節目的第二季<ref>{{cite web|last=|first=|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/newsbeat-29993873|title=Dapper Laughs: ITV2 says no second series for comedian|work=BBC news|date=2014-11-10|access-date=2021-06-28|archive-date=2021-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210628145939/https://www.bbc.com/news/newsbeat-29993873|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=|first=|url=https://www.itv.com/news/update/2014-11-10/itv-decides-not-to-continue-dapper-laughs-show/|title=Comedian Daniel O'Reilly retires Dapper Laughs|work=itv news|date=2014-11-10|access-date=2021-06-28|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513202407/https://www.itv.com/news/update/2014-11-10/itv-decides-not-to-continue-dapper-laughs-show/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

